{"id": 2028, "genre": 1001, "title": "从学校毕业之后，你觉得哪些东西其实还没学到位？", "description": "上学时候的这么多时间，都花到哪里了？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 3953, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171123142204la2mBE3QwWkhizKL.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-29T03:00:23Z", "options": [{"id": 251648, "content": "学校学的每一样东西吧，写题很溜，实际不会用", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074002}, {"id": 251904, "content": "专业知识吧，充其量入了个门，想装逼都不够?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 251649, "content": "勇气", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1193085}, {"id": 251650, "content": "逻辑思维能力，对未知领域的理解力和学习能力。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195181}, {"id": 251906, "content": "从脆弱中绝处逢生 才发现原来自己并不脆弱 内心强大才是生活积极的必经之路 一个女孩子不应该沉浸在一段无用的爱情之中 应该好好运动 好好赚钱 好好生活 好好学习 活到老学到老 不学不活容易老 Better  me ", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1199149}, {"id": 251651, "content": "把学校理想化的设计落地", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107477}, {"id": 251907, "content": "毕业了才知道，学校食堂饭菜真便宜", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1199167}, {"id": 251908, "content": "毕业了才知道，学校食堂饭菜真便宜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1199167}, {"id": 251653, "content": "自然的辞职", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185364}, {"id": 251909, "content": "毕业了才知道，学校食堂饭菜真便宜", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1199167}, {"id": 252165, "content": "职高虽说是比普高轻松，可是正真轻松时，能学到哪里去", "image": "img/option/option/20171201130902U81d6qDY3yxk0Zg4", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194030}, {"id": 251654, "content": "如何得到真正的自由？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176920}, {"id": 251910, "content": "毕业了才知道，学校饭菜真便宜", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1199167}, {"id": 251655, "content": "没有学到真正的知识技能，学到的都是一应付考试", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 187375}, {"id": 251911, "content": "无所事事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198401}, {"id": 252167, "content": "总在想怎样克服自己的不足，却没认真考虑过如何发挥自己的优势", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1200427}, {"id": 251656, "content": "如何谈恋爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1082931}, {"id": 251914, "content": "还没学会社交技能", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1199188}, {"id": 251659, "content": "工作了，经常要和同事领导喝酒，酒量没练好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1186458}, {"id": 251661, "content": "如何更好的生存下去", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979933}, {"id": 251662, "content": "找对象那个，努力工作就行了，对象国家会分配的，不要急", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141976}, {"id": 252175, "content": "如何更好地接纳自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1200443}, {"id": 259087, "content": "保持学习的动力\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236558}, {"id": 251664, "content": "学的是设计，学校学的课程特别多.觉得学那么多有啥用，专攻一门就可以了，然后毕业后所有公司都要求你什么都会，我却只会一门，然后苦逼的自学钻研，不好意思问老师，网上到处找资料自学", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1190195}, {"id": 251665, "content": "人际关系没有学到位。还有学到的职场知识都比较老旧，太单一，都是小儿科。在这个多变的时代，更多的还是自己摸索吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198417}, {"id": 251666, "content": "怎么知道自己想要什么，怎么去得到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198420}, {"id": 251922, "content": "如何做一个恰到好处的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974730}, {"id": 251667, "content": "我从驾校毕业了，可是我感觉我的倒车入库还没学好呢！怎么办呀？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198375}, {"id": 251668, "content": "没学到怎么学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1196822}, {"id": 252437, "content": "感觉什么都没学到位", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202712}, {"id": 252950, "content": "一个套适合自己的世界观价值观。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1204151}, {"id": 251671, "content": "怎样与他人相处，怎样与自己相处，怎样与自然和周围的环境相处", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198430}, {"id": 251930, "content": "学会拒绝，懂得接受", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1196195}, {"id": 252186, "content": "专业知识！！！人际关系！！！融资理财！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1165090}, {"id": 252954, "content": "社交能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205564}, {"id": 252444, "content": "交朋友能力永远重要  无论在哪工作 人都很需要朋友 因为我们都是群居动物！ 还有很多人凭借交际能力赚钱的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871583}, {"id": 251677, "content": "如何管理人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198439}, {"id": 252957, "content": "大学走出校门后，会让你感受到社会的复杂，社会的现实。人情的冷暖。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205564}, {"id": 251678, "content": "没有教会你怎么思考问题，怎么在复杂的事情中理清头绪，连英文也没有好好学", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761720}, {"id": 251680, "content": "毕业之后成长最快了，一下子理解很多事。说不出来的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194745}, {"id": 251681, "content": "拓展了很多东西，就是没学好专业课", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198441}, {"id": 252449, "content": "没有在大学弄清楚自己将来究竟要从事什么职业", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202964}, {"id": 251682, "content": "批判性思维", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772415}, {"id": 252962, "content": "如何判断心意的男神是否喜欢自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995495}, {"id": 251683, "content": "以后工作所需之用", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198450}, {"id": 252195, "content": "谈恋爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78222}, {"id": 251684, "content": "以后工作所需之用", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198450}, {"id": 252964, "content": "毕业进入社会，感觉大学什么都没学。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1196501}, {"id": 251685, "content": "学的东西可能很多都用来应付考试了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198461}, {"id": 251941, "content": "学校教你如何成为劳动的工具，而不是如何做一个人。可惜的是，有时他们前者教的也不怎么样", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1199314}]}